Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.56,0:00:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这片寂静撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.07,0:00:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引领整个世界\N来到炽热之焰的最深处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神Zwei
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将我们的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.39,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高举的愤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.63,0:00:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度点燃你的热情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸腾不已的火红热血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.61,0:00:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁都已无法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.44,0:00:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.82,0:01:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍卫弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.36,0:01:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈阳超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无畏惧的向前奔驰吧\N直到冲过那深红色的终点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.70,0:01:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最后一刻燃尽一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“粉碎的女神(机组)”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.45,0:02:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生...请问要用餐吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.76,0:02:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐身上\N没有出现任何异常情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意识无法恢复的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.47,0:02:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是来自于精神上的打击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.84,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐她现在\N正拒绝接受现实的世界...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个状况要是继续下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论莉露还是其他人都会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说都是斗牙的错吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过...那小子太搞不清楚状况了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.57,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不懂自己不经意所做的事\N到底会给对方带来多大的影响...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙也是以他的方式\N在关心着莉露呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.08,0:03:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他并不是有意的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才更饶不了他嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他总是那样一直笑着\N也想要当个乖宝宝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事情完全不是那么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那小子...\N他不知道什么叫痛苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了...够了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为从来都没有人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教他到底什么才叫做痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起战斗的方式...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该有更优先\N教会的事情才对吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...\N他已经一点一点的在改变了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在英司你来了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在莉露加入了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连斗牙自己都说\N他想要改变了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情为什么会变成这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他想自己一个人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露要是看到这些花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.04,0:04:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会不会高兴呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.09,0:04:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都这么不加思索的\N做了很伤人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.89,0:04:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到被英司这么骂了之后\N我才真的注意到这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就只会一直伤害大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却什么...什么都不能挽回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷原来您在这里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到斗牙少爷了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安抚斗牙少爷这件事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光凭我实在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这或许是我的错也不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我一直都伺候在他身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷才会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这样的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷能这么顺利的\N成长到今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这全都是靠爱娜的爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要自个儿硬钻牛角尖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是连你都开始心烦的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是反而让斗牙少爷\N感到更痛苦吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是媚月小姐能在的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种企图在废弃水霸上着陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因为干扰力场展开的影响\N无法掌握目前状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.48,0:06:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影与G打击机的\N幽灵系统搭载作业已经完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.42,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须有两部用幽灵出击啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重战骑们遭受打击的情形\N似乎也很严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的能够作战吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也别无他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全机出发准备完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重战骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G打击机 G攻击机\N出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影\NG钻机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现场的情形还不明朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.48,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外星异种分析结果出来前\N不要勉强进行攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20秒后将会到达现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.07,0:09:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然这么随便就打了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.34,0:09:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快点合神啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有两架是用幽灵系统不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神后的神机超重神出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.49,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有平时的61.9%...\N这样风险相当大!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神...不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先观察一下情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交由各机判断各自进行攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.53,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干扰力场消失!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有一大堆什么东西耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请求照准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重战骑的诸位\N启动合神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这种手段...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太龌龊了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然是\N瞄准了合神的那一瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁机封印住超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种...开始侵蚀超重皇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种...开始吸取\N超重皇的重力子能源了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去\N驾驶员会无法承受负荷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗...斗牙少爷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.18,0:12:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西!\N打算把超重皇生吞活剥吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们左右包抄它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把外星异种从斗牙身上剥下来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃弹头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快照我的意思去动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法\N这样子根本无法靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...再这样下去的话斗牙就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜! 爱娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊...超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把我...杀了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.46,0:13:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去的话\N超重皇会继续失控的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把地球变的和兰比亚斯一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有驾驶员\N超重皇应该就会停止行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.71,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样因为我的关系\N而伤害到大家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在鬼扯什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我振作点斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把你救出来的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.35,0:14:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有办法...保护别人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不用再勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们快动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙我现在就赶过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有实现和你的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜...你要做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.08,0:14:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种正从超重皇内\N吸取重力子能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要直接与其接触\N并让被抽取出来的能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.39,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入G钻机的重力子循环系统\N并在增幅后反馈回去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.77,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许就能救出斗牙少爷了\N也说不定...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情...有可能办到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是让我去的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.88,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是桑德曼先生\N创造出来的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"原型.超重机组"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"原型.超重机组"?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜开始转换为\N原初.超重机组模式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快切断转换!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.06,0:15:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有效!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部超重机组都无法控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.97,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有机能都被爱娜遮蔽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G钻机在执行分离程序?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?无法操作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱...爱娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷他...就麻烦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜你想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.43,0:16:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋为什么动不了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司快阻止她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.21,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜她想要牺牲自己!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜不要这样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你快点回来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的一切...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了斗牙少爷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.52,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您要活下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是...真的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶! 那混蛋居然还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.38,0:18:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机体还...可恶\N为什么都没有反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点动快点动啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙快逃啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重钻机...左侧驾驶舱\N反应消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.31,0:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员...没有回应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.11,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样?连琉菜小姐也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要...我不要这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星辰群光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击阵列V
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电光雷管!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JACKOFF(回家吃自己吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好强喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.08,0:20:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EFA的量产型超重神...\N已经完成了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.08,0:21:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是...你所追求的东西吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是超重要塞\N开始回收超重皇与G攻击机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医疗班请立即待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武装女仆班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.99,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在现场散开后开始搜救G钻机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请以这项任务为第一优先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好强喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是...我们的力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.74,0:21:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然就只有这点斤两吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼和计算中的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人期待的是以后的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重...皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星辰群光结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯旋归建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是空的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.04,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因热恋而无法成眠的夜晚\N已经看腻了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.55,0:22:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为想要听到人的声音\N所以随意打了电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.93,0:22:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了靠不住的语音留言\N你现在到底在哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.54,0:22:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映着冰箱内的灯光\N我在狭小的宇宙里彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.41,0:22:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我的唱片\N唱针已经跳开不知几次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.88,0:22:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信这不变的温度\N一直到什么时候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.36,0:22:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.96,0:22:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳边轻语嘛\N对让我听听你温柔的声音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.47,0:22:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们手牵着手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.44,0:23:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N浅浅呼吸笼罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.98,0:23:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳边轻语嘛\N对让我听听你温柔的声音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.65,0:23:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们闭上双眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.59,0:23:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜进你梦里的\N甜美节奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.94,0:23:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了啦\N再哭爱娜也一样回不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.47,0:23:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.54,0:23:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚娘、布丽姬妲、雪希尔\N你们振作点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.04,0:23:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要连爱娜的份\N一起努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.55,0:23:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...英司少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.21,0:23:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.32,0:23:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不见了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.88,0:23:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.72,0:23:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回\N“在重力衰弱的时刻”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.42,0:23:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回我们也要照料各位的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜姊...